
  # Podcast Profile Dashboard

  This is a code bundle for Podcast Profile Dashboard. The original project is available at https://www.figma.com/design/0QHyOF3CmEU2MamWEHQNHY/Podcast-Profile-Dashboard.

  ## Running the code

  Run `npm i` to install the dependencies.

  Run `npm run dev` to start the development server.
